MLModelDescriptionKey: An updatable model which can be used to train a tiny 28 x 28 drawing classifier based on user examples. It uses a drawing embedding trained on the Quick, Draw! dataset (https://github.com/googlecreativelab/quickdraw-dataset)
MLModelLicenseKey: https://docs-assets.developer.apple.com/coreml/models/Image/DrawingClassification/UpdatableDrawingClassifier/LICENSE-MIT.txt For information about the dataset, please see https://github.com/googlecreativelab/quickdraw-dataset.
